node.text: What an amazing trip from BKK to LA to SF to Mexico City to Chicago to Columbus... got to see so many loved ones and experience once in a lifetime moments like @ravipatelll‘s wedding and Teotihuacán / @juanglez7’s 29th 😂:) #lax #sfo #mex #ord #cmh #bkk
So good seeing you and glad you had an awesome trip!
@juanglez7 — aren’t you one of the luchadores ?? 😂🔥
How come I am not in any of the pictures? You came for my birthday... I feel used
Love you boo come back please 😍💝

Vicool! I’m glad you had a great trip! Please come back to Mexico soon. That was such a fun weekend.
Also, I think that pyramid is looking pretty amazing with us in front of it 😊 and our picture easily outshines any of the real-couples pictures jajaja
